  "name": "build-a-fail-closed-20260409-2327",
  "idea": "Build a fail-closed generalized payment subsystem for ArcCompute-style payouts on Solana. Replace direct grant sends with a reusable payment ledger, provider abstraction, wallet registry, Discord confirmation flow, manual hold/retry controls, and restart-safe recovery. Critical requirements: no automatic double-payment after tx submission unless chain definitively reports failure; ambiguous chain state freezes to manual hold; private keys never enter DB/logs/admin-chat; atomic worker claiming; separate test-payment and final-payment attempts; grants becomes a producer into the payment system.",
